I've been playing this game for 2 years now, only game that has ever had my attention this long.

TO THE DEVELOPERS - It would be awesome if you could watch the entire game in a replay, or at least watching the last 2-3 moves per player, not just the previous turn.

Also, adding an ability to keep score against players you play with over and over again would make this game twice as addictive.

This game is one of the most challenging games I have ever played. One thing that you could fix or tweak though, would have to be the "jump" power up. It kind of ruins the concept of the game when you jump all the way across the map for the win. Also, one thing you could change would be to put the power ups up and down the side of the screen instead of having to flip through a cycle deal. Another thing to include would be maybe a loop or two and some new maps.Other than that, this app is one great game.
